<br>
Unfortunately I don't quite have my list on me just now but depending on what grimling you kill depends on what runes you get.<br>
<br>
The Grimling Orefinders and Grimling Geomancers are the common spawns followed by Grimling Foreman.<br>
<br>
There also seem to be a couple of other Grimlings but these ones always spawn at the back of the cave and then wander out the cave and wander about outside the cave. One of these is the Grimling Laborer and only this one seems to drop Etched Acrylia Rune : Amn.<br>
<br>
the other wanderer is the Grimling Runner which drops part of the Rallic Pack quest and also occasionally some runes. This one only spawned twice for me so I'm not totally sure what runes drop off this one. Mind you I now have components to make two attempts at the Rallic pack. <br>
<br>
I have already made a tentative attempt at combining and so far Words of Bondage doesn't mix with any of these runes in the box you get off the sage. I am going to hopefully try and do a bit of combining with these runes and the necro 44th and possibly chanter 39th and 44th words and pages. I will post tomorrow with my results. I will try and combine them in both the box and the Grimoire just in case.<br>
<br>
If anyone else manages to find any information regarding these runes please post something.<br>
<br>
It is always possible that only a wizzie can combine these runes since runes are normally wizzie research items but I hope this isn't the case since I'm a magician. &lt;chuckles&gt;<br>
<br>
Wabbus<br>
